{"tid":2402642,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"14歲男童掟汽油彈被控暴動 練錦鴻:怎樣一時衝動? 校長:日後願重新面試被告 給予返回學校機會","createTime":"2021-02-10T14:11:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-10T18:05:40.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"d7cecf624d29f35726976b6109044935f3768ad0","tid":2402642,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T14:11:57.000Z","msg":"14歲少年前年11月16日凌晨參與旺角街頭示威，逃避警方掃蕩時投擲一枚汽油彈，汽油彈著地起火，少年最後被防暴警察擒獲。他承認暴動和企圖縱火罪，辯方今於區域法院求情，指少年精於體育和音樂，一時衝動愚蠢犯案；當日有人將汽油彈交給他，他沒想清楚後果便掟出去，望法庭念在他年輕，而且被捕後坦白承認作為，判處更生性質的院所刑罰。法官練錦鴻先索取背景、勞教中心和教導所報告，少年還柙至下月3日判刑。<br />\n<br />\n警方施行警誡前查問被告，被告表示有人教他投擲汽油彈，士巴拿則用作拆除圍欄。警誡會面期間，被告承認和4至5名朋友站在彌敦道，警方發出警告後他沒有離開，原因是沒看見有人離開。及後有人給他汽油彈，教他擲到地上。士巴拿則非他所有，而是有人放進其背包內。<br />\n<br />\n庭上播放控方賴以為證據的新聞直播片段。法官練錦鴻要求查看被告的頭盔、背包、防毒面具、手套等證物，一一從證物袋拆出仔細觀察，又用手敲打頭盔。<br />\n<br />\n被告本人、父母、鋼琴老師、籃球教練、班主任及社工等人向法庭呈交求情信，讚揚被告為人認真有禮，連年參加音樂比賽，並準備應考7級鋼琴試。<br />\n<br />\n辯方又指，籃球教練表示被告一時衝動做出蠢事。法官聞言，問辯方怎樣一時衝動，辯方解釋指「另一個人畀個汽油彈佢，就掟咗出去」，強調被告已深感懊悔，被捕當日馬上坦白招認，上庭後第一時間認罪。<br />\n<br />\n辯方續說，被告有接受輔導，社工指他承認迷失，反省後已明白學生的責任。專家形容被告有良好進步，班主任亦稱被告性情有明顯轉變，有強烈悔意，努力尋找自我控制和補救的方法。校長表明，日後願重新面試被告，給予返回學校的機會。父母亦願意與被告一起接受為期至少一年的輔導。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210210/WAM25XLUUBH4XGITIRCUEGWW2A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210210%2FWAM25XLUUBH4XGITIRCUEGWW2A%2F&d=9j7BdtwWq97OJFdF2FXGhdOJZs7QJHlESVJdSYWWwTM%3D&h=f5b99b75\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210210%2FWAM25XLUUBH4XGITIRCUEGWW2A%2F&h=7e6fe34d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210210/WAM25XLUUBH4XGITIRCUEGWW2A/</a>"},{"pid":"0461dffc69f87bf428ee04f0d019fdb22e550a73","tid":2402642,"uid":204231,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T14:12:29.000Z","msg":"練狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"931070145b9e369492567b88dc0ab8637ae15572","tid":2402642,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T14:17:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e67100390fccd3424f1e826bfe0994bee726cf7f","tid":2402642,"uid":358691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T14:33:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d5c797be69c283e6f678bf248f9b3c38e887909","tid":2402642,"uid":126919,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T14:37:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7cf44068326e96bdc81508a87a2f37cbb36ea83","tid":2402642,"uid":311128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T14:39:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"803b259cf8e188400e897043304da867c501c50f","tid":2402642,"uid":235535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T14:40:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2539d0f9e685f6d5d5dc6411a3360386f40153a3","tid":2402642,"uid":305767,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T14:41:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />練狗"}